OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773774690
OL,3,CJersey Sport calls for new strategy to
OL,4,Cbecome an 'active tourism' hotspot
OL,6,FJersey's Sports Council is calling on
OL,7,Fthe island's government to channel
OL,8,Fmore money into local sporting events
OL,9,Fand competitions - arguing they could
OL,10,Fbe one solution to declining tourist
OL,11,Fnumbers.
OL,13,FIt comes after the number of Jersey
OL,14,Fvisitors fell sharply in 2025, most
OL,15,Fnotably falling by a fifth in August
OL,16,Fthat year when compared to August 2024.
OL,18,FThe Council says Jersey is well-placed
OL,19,Fto host international sporting
OL,20,Fcompetitions and attract both athletes
OL,21,Fand spectators throughout the year.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773774690
OL,3,CJersey Sport calls for new strategy to
OL,4,Cbecome an 'active tourism' hotspot
OL,6,FHowever, they say this is too often
OL,7,Fdone without any financial assistance
OL,8,Ffrom the States of Jersey.
OL,10,FIan Cumming, Chair of the Jersey
OL,11,FSports Council, says the island needs
OL,12,Fto "rethink" its overarching tourism
OL,13,Fstrategy.
OL,15,F"At the moment, it's sold very much on
OL,16,Fsun, sea, sand, our restaurants, the
OL,17,Fcountryside," Ian told ITV News.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773774690
OL,3,CJersey Sport calls for new strategy to
OL,4,Cbecome an 'active tourism' hotspot
OL,6,F"I think we should broaden our
OL,7,Fstrategy so instead of just looking
OL,8,Ffor sun, sea, and sand - if people
OL,9,Fwant that, they can go to the
OL,10,FMediterranean - let's go for those
OL,11,Fpeople who want an active lifestyle.
OL,13,F"There are so many different sports
OL,14,Fwhich a holidaymaker could come across
OL,15,F- either as an individual, or a group,
OL,16,For as part of a major sporting event -
OL,17,Fand they bring family and friends and
OL,18,Fsupporters. This could bring tourism
OL,19,Fthroughout the year.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773774690
OL,3,CJersey Sport calls for new strategy to
OL,4,Cbecome an 'active tourism' hotspot
OL,6,F"It's not always a lot of money that
OL,7,Fneeds to be spent, but certainly
OL,8,Fgiving help with promotion would be a
OL,9,Fuseful way of spending government
OL,10,Fmoney."
OL,12,FAccording to Visit Jersey, sports
OL,13,Ftourism accounted for 4% of total
OL,14,Fvisitors to the island in 2025, with
OL,15,Fthe majority staying for a couple of
OL,16,Fdays.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773774690
OL,3,CJersey Sport calls for new strategy to
OL,4,Cbecome an 'active tourism' hotspot
OL,6,FFor example, the 50-Over International
OL,7,FCricket Council Challenge League saw
OL,8,Fplayers spend a combined total of
OL,9,F1,000 nights in hotels across the
OL,10,Fisland.
OL,12,FSarah Gomershall, CEO of Jersey
OL,13,FCricket, says it cost "just shy of
OL,14,F#500,000" to host the event, but
OL,15,F"didn't get any government financial
OL,16,Fsupport".
OL,18,FWhilst Sarah says they broadly receive
OL,19,Fa lot of government support, she feels
OL,20,F"there are currently opportunities to
OL,21,Fbe missed".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773774690
OL,3,CJersey Sport calls for new strategy to
OL,4,Cbecome an 'active tourism' hotspot
OL,6,F"Outside of the practicality of
OL,7,Fplaying sport, strategically, they
OL,8,Fdon't seem to have a plan of how to
OL,9,Fleverage sport from a sport tourism
OL,10,Fperspective," Sarah told ITV News.
OL,12,F"There is an opportunity to do more
OL,13,Fjoined-up thinking, and particularly
OL,14,Fbring Jersey Sport into that
OL,15,Fconversation - to get the people in
OL,16,Fsport leadership around the table to
OL,17,Fsee what we can do."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773774690
OL,3,CJersey Sport calls for new strategy to
OL,4,Cbecome an 'active tourism' hotspot
OL,6,FJersey's Infrastructure Minister,
OL,7,FDeputy Andy Jehan, says work is being
OL,8,Fdone to capitalise on these kinds of
OL,9,Fsports events and competitions.
OL,11,F"Sports tourism is really important.
OL,12,FWe have a number of our team sports
OL,13,Fattract visitors on a weekly basis,
OL,14,Fand we're trying to help events in the
OL,15,Fshoulder months in particular", Deputy
OL,16,FJehan said.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773774690
OL,3,CJersey Sport calls for new strategy to
OL,4,Cbecome an 'active tourism' hotspot
OL,6,F"We are supporting sport, and this
OL,7,Fyear we hope to put one million pounds
OL,8,Finto sport - and in addition to that,
OL,9,Fthe Government are looking to put in
OL,10,Faround #130,000 to promote sporting
OL,11,Fevents on the island."
OL,13,FThe Minister added the island can
OL,14,F"improve in terms of promoting events
OL,15,Fon-island to off-island people", but
OL,16,Fhopes Visit Jersey and Jersey Sport
OL,17,Fcould soon adopt "a consistent
OL,18,Fapproach" or coordinated sports
OL,19,Ftourism strategy.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
